HEADWORD: Nosing
<hw>Nos"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Arch.)</fld>
<def>That part of the treadboard of a stair which projects over the
riser; hence, any like projection, as the projecting edge of a
molding.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nosle</ent>⟦br⟧
